      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. Everything runs smoothly and it's ready for its next adventure! Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 29500.0,
