    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused F80 M3 featuring the S55 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six powerplant, utilizing a closed-deck block design and wire-arc sprayed cylinder bores for enhanced structural rigidity. This unit delivers a relentless torque curve through a precision 6-speed manual transmission, paired with a carbon fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) driveshaft for reduced rotational inertia. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, benefiting from M-specific suspension kinematics and an Active M Differential that provides proactive locking for superior traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul and fresh bushings. While the exterior shows honest signs of spirited road use, the mechanical vitals are robust, ensuring the high-revving engagement and lateral G-loading capabilities synonymous with the M badge.",
